{"body": "You can create app using old hash syntax:\r\n\r\n```\r\nrails new example --old-style-hash\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf you are using rails master you can add it to the .railsrc file in your user home dir and it will be set as default for all your new applications:\r\n\r\n```\r\n--old-style-hash\r\n```\r\n\r\nIn general is a good idea use same version of Ruby in development machine and in servers", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2298710", "created_at": "2011-10-05T14:50:03Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/542#issuecomment-2298710", "updated_at": "2011-10-05T14:52:19Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 542, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/guilleiguaran", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/73d57855a3bfe5c534596197a895ab6e?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ffa159acecc4c559601c9a2fc35c75213.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/received_events", "gravatar_id": "73d57855a3bfe5c534596197a895ab6e", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "guilleiguaran", "type": "User", "id": 160941, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/guilleiguaran/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52385e7abd3543c151012084"}, "id": 2298710, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/542"}
